flowchart LR
    C[应用客户端] --> B[Primary Backend]
    B --> SB[shared_buffers]
    B --> WB[WAL Buffers]
    WB --> PW[Primary pg_wal / WAL Flush]

    PW --> WS[WAL Sender]
    WS -->|WAL Stream| WR[Standby WAL Receiver]
    WR --> SW[Standby pg_wal]
    SW --> SP[Startup Process]
    SP --> RBUF[Standby shared_buffers / Data Files]
    RBUF --> Q[Hot Standby Read Query]

    WR -->|write / flush / replay feedback| WS
    WS -.同步提交确认.-> B

    SLOT[Physical Replication Slot] -.保护 restart_lsn 之后的 WAL.-> PW
    VAC[Primary VACUUM / DDL] --> PW
    SP -.Recovery Conflict.-> Q
